{"tid":1884953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓逾30車相撞最少三死","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T04:38:20.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec75bd3e284c78783a95d208105478747be2340","tid":1884953,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓西北部一條隧道有30多輛車連環相撞，包括運載化學品的油罐車，造成最少三人死亡，四十多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n隧道內的閉路電視拍攝到，位於全羅北道由順天市至完州郡的高速公路隧道內開始塞車，先有尾隨的私家車收掣不及追撞前方車輛，後來再有兩輛大型貨車高速撞向車群，其中一輛相信是載有近二萬公升硝酸的油罐車，它流出化學品觸發大火，濃煙不斷由隧道口冒出。<br />\n<br />\n意外在周一中午十二時半左右發生，隧道附近隨即充斥有毒氣體，八十輛消防車及二百多人到場救援，死者包括油罐車司機，警方正調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場一帶凌晨開始下大雪，路面平滑，有司機憶述剎車時，車子仍然會滑行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=380999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380999&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6cd7758f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380999&h=c5101b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=380999</a>"},{"pid":"3e94580e892fbb5e66b6f275b78d8a6cafd4be98","tid":1884953,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"漏nitric acid?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c1ada80e13115ba5522d3dff9524f8889d2f41","tid":1884953,"uid":245421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"危險品車輛入隧道真係好高風險，有事無人走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0befabdfca60b21a7e8419e857ac93486fbdbae7","tid":1884953,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"願平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif